# Project Structure

This is a full-stack application with separate frontend and backend directories.

## Frontend Structure
- `frontend/src/` - Main source code directory
  - `presentation/` - React components and pages
    - `pages/` - Main page components
    - `components/` - Reusable UI components
    - `contexts/` - React context providers
    - `routes/` - Application routing configuration
  - `services/` - API service classes
  - `i18n/` - Internationalization files
  - `shared-theme/` - Theme configuration and components

## Backend Structure
- `backend/app/` - Main application code
  - `api/` - API endpoints and controllers
  - `core/` - Core business logic
  - `models/` - Database models
  - `services/` - Business services
  - `utils/` - Utility functions

## Key Files
- [frontend/src/presentation/routes/index.tsx](mdc:frontend/src/presentation/routes/index.tsx) - Main routing configuration
